You hit like a drunk cigarette
The feeling amplified
By saying things we never meant
(Oh yeah)

You leave me filled with regret
At the end of the night
I always find myself wondering why
(Oh yeah)

Do you got plans for life
Cause I don’t wanna just romance tonight
I wanna see you in another light (oh yeah)
With rhythm there is rhyme
With you there always can be I
I wanna see you in another light (ooh)

I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a homewrecker
I just know I can be better, be better, be better
I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a broken record
I just know I can be better, be better, be better

We sit on the fire escape
We talk and talk ‘till dawn
I open up to you about my wrongs
(Oh yeah)

Then we lay and contemplate
Just one more round of love
Before you go home to another one

Do you got plans for life
Cause I don’t wanna just romance tonight
I wanna see you in another light (oh yeah)
With rhythm there is rhyme
With you there always can be I
I wanna see you in another light (ooh)

I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a homewrecker
I just know I can be better, be better, be better
I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a broken record
I just know I can be better, be better, be better

I don’t wanna be how you formulate opinions on astrology (oh no)
Or to say we made peace and then your friends don’t even wanna talk to me no more
No more
I wanna kiss you on the bed and on the floor
When I’m poor, when I’m bored
I am yours, I am yours, I am yours

I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a homewrecker
I just know I can be better, be better, be better
I don’t wanna talk down on your lover
I don’t wanna be a broken record
I just know I can be better, be better, be better

snippet.title: Minecraft Trapper VS 1000 Players
snippet.description:
On the world's largest Hardcore Minecraft server, I challenged 1000 players to try to ban me off the Unstable SMP. This is my story of how I fought back as a Minecraft Trapper...

Minecraft Trapper VS 1000 Players

inspired by @JudeLoSasso's MrBeast 1000 players video!

Unstable SMP Members
➜ @wemmbumc 
➜ @FlameFragsMC 
➜ @ParrotX2 
➜ @Spokeishere 




possible spoilers below this point

trap designs:
Arrow Railgun: @Glue_IsSticky @croak14 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfW9ZasLQBs
8x8 Piston Fall Trap: @ShadowKiller_NM https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=okdsyn196sA
Landmines: @Ro11enYT https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UxJj766xgCI
Invisible Chest Void Trap: @jojosolos https://www.youtube.com/shorts/lsF_juE6UOI
TNT Railgun: @justwhitevoid https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ISAqBQ5ejw

features: @MapiccMc @PrinceZam @Leowook + a surprise guest....

music: 
Ivory /  @ivoryfrill  &  @MythrodakTV  
DM DOKURO /  @DMDOKURO  
Chris Christodoulou /  @AstronautDown  
Pascal Stiefel /  @Plasma3Music  
Lena Raine / @LenaRaine 
C418 / @C418
Peter McConnell

This is a video on the Unstable Universe: a staged Minecraft server where Spoke, Wemmbu, FlameFrags, and ParrotX2 aim to tell the best stories possible. btw a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

written, recorded, & edited by spoke

snippet.title: Viah (Official Video) Arzz Singh l Ft. Sukmani Narula & Puneet Dung l Sadiorafilmz l Rammy Records
snippet.description:
Rammy Records Presents – Viah 

Step back into the golden era of the 90s with Viah a beautifully crafted vintage wedding song that celebrates love, emotions, and timeless traditions.

Sung, written, and composed with heart by Arzz, this soulful track captures the purity of old-school romance, brought alive through rich melodies and heartfelt lyrics. Featuring Sukhmani Narula and Puneet, the visuals add grace and charm to this emotional wedding journey. Cinematically filmed by Sadiora Filmz, Viah blends classic aesthetics with modern storytelling, creating a truly nostalgic and soulful experience.

snippet.title: EXIT 8 - Official Trailer - In Theaters April 10
snippet.description: Based on the global hit eponymous video game created by KOTAKE CREATE. A man trapped in an endless sterile subway passageway sets out to find Exit 8. The rules of his quest are simple: do not overlook anything out of the ordinary. If you discover an anomaly, turn back immediately. If you don’t, carry on. Then leave from Exit 8. But even a single oversight will send him back to the beginning. Will he ever reach his goal and escape this infinite corridor?

snippet.title: Timberborn 1.0 Release Date & Lore Trailer
snippet.description:
💥 Join beavers braving the post-human wasteland in our official lore trailer... and find out when Timberborn 1.0 goes live!

Learn more below:
https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1062090/view/526491913334818791

This video is narrated by none other than Shaun Dooley (Elden Ring, Netflix's Witcher series).

Trailer by Lost Cosmonauts. Music by Jeffrey 'Pumodi' Brice.

-- About Timberborn --
Humans are long gone. In a world struck by droughts and toxic waste, will your lumberpunk beavers do any better? A sandbox city-building game featuring ingenious animals, vertical architecture, water physics, and terraforming. Contains high amounts of wood.

snippet.title: One Mile | Official Trailer | Paramount Movies
snippet.description:
ONE MILE: CHAPTER ONE
Ryan Phillippe stars as a former special forces operative trying to reconnect with his teenage daughter during a college road trip. When an unexpected detour puts them in the sights of a secretive, off-the-grid community, his daughter is taken and the trip erupts into a high-octane fight for survival. Alone and outnumbered, he’s forced to use every skill he has to track them down, take them apart, and bring his daughter home.

ONE MILE: CHAPTER TWO
A former special forces operative (Ryan Phillippe) is forced back onto a remote island when the violent, secretive community he fought once before abducts his daughter in an act of revenge. Launched into a relentless hunt, he faces an enemy that’s ready and anticipating his every move.

Alone and outnumbered, he’s forced to use every skill he has to track them down, take them apart, and bring his daughter home.

A former special forces operative (Ryan Phillippe) is forced back onto a remote island when the violent, secretive community he fought once before abducts his daughter in an act of revenge. Launched into a relentless hunt, he faces an enemy that’s ready and anticipating his every move.
